ntrol</span><hr size=1> I see the top agro weapons post and have read through it, but I'm afraid I must admit that I am not as rich/old as other warriors who post here (This is one of the things that makes this site so valuable to me, but for this situation is a hindrance.) and can't drop 30K because I only have 3K. I am a level 51 Warrior on Tholuxxe Paells in a feeder guild. I know that once I ding 55 I will not be able to ever MA again since so many other more experienced warriors with better equipment will be ahead of me in the ranks. But, for now since 55 is high end for the feeder I am starting to get SA and AA assignments, and last night I MA'd for the first time in the Plate House. I loved it and felt I did a good job taking the hits etcetera, but man I had to FIGHT to hold agro. Right now I wield a Jade Mace and Lammy and I'm getting the feeling that soon these weapons just aren't goin to do it as far as keeping agro. Can anyone here suggest agro weapons that would be affordable to me? I can forsee raising another 2K if necessary to bring my spendable cash to 5K. Any ehlp would be great I won't be in the posittion to be an MA for long and while I have the chance I want to be a good one. Thank you for any wisdom the soldiers who read this sight might offer.<br>
<br>
