I agree with the previous poster. BBoT is a great aggro getter if it procs. I posted here a few weeks ago with a similar request and was recommended the BBoT. For the cash, it is excellent imo.<br>
<br>
In a HoT raid I was at, the first three tanks went down due to huge screw ups. I threw up defensive (down to one cleric, we only had two to begin with) and mainhanded this with the snare whip offhand, which is not the greatest aggro combo compared to others that you will see here. Even defensive, I was able to keep aggro well enough to stop the ping ponging and let the casters do their thing.<br>
<br>
Just one of my experiences.<br>
