a good combo for agro into your late 50s and do decent damage.  Depending on your server economy, it should be fairly painless to save up for these in a couple weeks time.  Cost would be about 3500 for the frostbringer, and ~4k for the anklesmasher on my server.  Just coerce a druid/shaman/cleric to go farm HGs with you for a couple days <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Guard captains mallet, bloodpoint and fungus encrusted hammer are decent and reasonably priced also.<br>
